OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry day, bright with
OL,6,Fsome hazy sunny intervals but in
OL,7,Fgeneral a lot of cloud, perhaps a spot
OL,8,For two of rain over western counties.
OL,9,FFreshening southerly wind.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry through the evening,
OL,12,Fquite cloudy at first but with
OL,13,Fincreasingly clear skies. Staying
OL,14,Fmostly dry overnight, with just the
OL,15,Fodd shower possible around dawn.
OL,16,FBreezy, especially around the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
