OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMostly dry, bright and quite
OL,6,Fwarm in the morning, but chance of the
OL,7,Fodd shower. Cloudier later with
OL,8,Fshowery rain. Breezy morning,
OL,9,Fespecially around coasts, winds
OL,10,Fbecoming light later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,13,Fbright Wednesday morning, cloudier
OL,14,Fwith patchy rain later. Cooler with
OL,15,Fsunshine and showers on Thursday. Wet
OL,16,Fand windy on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
